              <span class="text-blue-600 font-serif text-xl block mb-2">Day 4</span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Ubud ‚Üí Amed</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Scenic drive to the east coast via Sidemen road, passing ancient courts and bat caves.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 border border-stone-100 shadow-sm w-full">
                <ul class="text-stone-500 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-500">‚Ä¢</span> Stop at Kerta Gosa (Ancient Justice Court)</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-500">‚Ä¢</span> Visit Goa Lawah (Bat Cave Temple)</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-500">‚Ä¢</span> Kusamba salt farming village</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 5 -->
          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 timeline-item">
            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-blue-500 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1.5 mt-6 border-4 border-stone-50 z-10 timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="pl-12 md:pl-0 md:pr-12 md:text-right md:col-start-1 md:row-start-1">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-serif text-xl block mb-2">Day 5</span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Amed Ocean & Culture</h3>
