                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-500">‚Ä¢</span> Visit Lempuyang Temple (Gate of Heaven)</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-500">‚Ä¢</span> Tirta Gangga Water Palace</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-500">‚Ä¢</span> Sunset drinks at Jemeluk Bay</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SIDEMEN SECTION -->
        <div class="relative mb-20 timeline-section">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-12 relative z-10">
            <div class="bg-stone-50 px-6 py-2 border border-sage-500/30 text-sage-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full">
              Sidemen ‚Ä¢ Days 6-7
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 6 -->
          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16 timeline-item">
            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-sage-500 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1.5 mt-6 border-4 border-stone-50 z-10 timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="pl-12 md:pl-12 md:col-start-2">
              <span class="text-sage-600 font-serif text-xl block mb-2">Day 6</span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Amed ‚Üí Sidemen</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Short drive to the lush green valley of Sidemen.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 border border-stone-100 shadow-sm w-full">
                <ul class="text-stone-500 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-sage-500">‚Ä¢</span> Check-in to bamboo villa or boutique resort</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-sage-500">‚Ä¢</span> Village walk and weaving workshop</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-sage-500">‚Ä¢</span> Relax by the river</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 7 -->
          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 timeline-item">
            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-sage-500 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1.5 mt-6 border-4 border-stone-50 z-10 timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="pl-12 md:pl-0 md:pr-12 md:text-right md:col-start-1 md:row-start-1">
              <span class="text-sage-600 font-serif text-xl block mb-2">Day 7</span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Sidemen Immersion</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Deep dive into Balinese rural life.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 border border-stone-100 shadow-sm inline-block text-left w-full">
                <ul class="text-stone-500 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-sage-500">‚Ä¢</span> Sunrise trekking in rice fields</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-sage-500">‚Ä¢</span> Traditional cooking class with local family</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-sage-500">‚Ä¢</span> Blessing ceremony with local priest</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-sage-500">‚Ä¢</span> Gembleng Waterfall visit</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ULUWATU SECTION -->
        <div class="relative timeline-section">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-12 relative z-10">
            <div class="bg-stone-50 px-6 py-2 border border-amber-500/30 text-amber-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full">
              Uluwatu ‚Ä¢ Days 8-11
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 8 -->
          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16 timeline-item">
            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1.5 mt-6 border-4 border-stone-50 z-10 timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="pl-12 md:pl-12 md:col-start-2">
              <span class="text-amber-600 font-serif text-xl block mb-2">Day 8</span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Sidemen ‚Üí Uluwatu</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Drive south to the Bukit Peninsula.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 border border-stone-100 shadow-sm w-full">
                <ul class="text-stone-500 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Stop at Sanur for lunch</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Check-in at cliffside or beach resort</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Sunset drinks at Rock Bar or similar</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 9 -->
          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16 timeline-item">
            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1.5 mt-6 border-4 border-stone-50 z-10 timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="pl-12 md:pl-0 md:pr-12 md:text-right md:col-start-1 md:row-start-1">
              <span class="text-amber-600 font-serif text-xl block mb-2">Day 9</span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Beach & Culture</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Explore the best beaches and culture of the south.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 border border-stone-100 shadow-sm inline-block text-left w-full">
                <ul class="text-stone-500 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Melasti or Padang Padang Beach</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Uluwatu Temple visit</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Kecak Fire Dance at sunset</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Seafood dinner at Jimbaran Bay</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 10 -->
          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16 timeline-item">
            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1.5 mt-6 border-4 border-stone-50 z-10 timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="pl-12 md:pl-12 md:col-start-2">
              <span class="text-amber-600 font-serif text-xl block mb-2">Day 10</span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Relaxation & Farewell</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                A final day of pure relaxation.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 border border-stone-100 shadow-sm w-full">
                <ul class="text-stone-500 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Spa treatment</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Sunday Beach Club or similar</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500">‚Ä¢</span> Farewell dinner</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 11 -->
          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 timeline-item">
